---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import inicio from "../assets/inicio.webp";
---

<section
  id="inicio"
  class="pt-24 pb-16 md:pt-32 md:pb-24
         bg-linear-to-br from-gray-50 via-green-50 to-white
         dark:from-[rgb(var(--surface))] dark:via-[rgb(var(--surface-muted))] dark:to-[rgb(var(--surface-card))]
         transition-colors duration-300"
>
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <span
          class="bg-green-100 dark:bg-[rgb(var(--surface-card))]
                 text-green-700 dark:text-[rgb(var(--accent-strong))]
                 border border-green-200 dark:border-[rgb(var(--border))]
                 px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-medium inline-block
                 shadow-sm dark:shadow-md transition-all duration-300"
        >
          ✨ Soluciones de Software Innovadoras
        </span>

        <h1
          class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold
                 text-[rgb(var(--text-primary))] dark:text-[rgb(var(--text-primary))]
                 leading-tight tracking-tight"
        >
          Transformamos tus ideas en
          <span
            class="bg-linear-to-r from-green-600 via-green-500 to-emerald-600
                   dark:from-green-400 dark:via-green-500 dark:to-emerald-400
                   bg-clip-text text-transparent"
          >
            software excepcional
          </span>
        </h1>

        <p
          class="text-lg text-[rgb(var(--text-muted))] dark:text-[rgb(var(--text-muted))] leading-relaxed"
        >
          Desarrollamos soluciones tecnológicas a medida que impulsan el
          crecimiento de tu negocio. Desde aplicaciones web hasta sistemas
          empresariales complejos.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
        <div
          class="absolute inset-0
                 bg-linear-to-br from-green-400/20 to-emerald-400/20
                 dark:from-green-500/10 dark:to-emerald-500/10
                 rounded-3xl blur-3xl"
        >
        </div>
        <Image
          src={inicio}
          alt="Nuestro equipo de desarrollo de software"
          class="relative w-full h-auto object-cover rounded-2xl"
          width={600}
          height={400}
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
